
EGlib works on every ST computer from the STF to the Falcon. The purpose of EGlib is to built a similar interface on any machine.
EGlib handles all the GEM programming (windows, menu, desk, messages, etc...), online help, keyboard, memory and other usefull functions.
The best configuration to use EGlib is 640x400 or more screen size with 16 or more colors with ›s_GDOS›SpeedoGDOS›u›.

